FBIS3-38914 "drweu027_p_94001" FBIS-WEU-94-027 Document Type:Daily Report 9 Feb 1994 GREECE Leaders Comment on EU Communique on Bosnia Pangalos: Peaceful Solution Sought NC0902061294 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network in Greek 0500 GMT 9 Feb 94 NC0902061294 Athens Elliniki Radhiofonia Radio Network Language: Greek Article Type:BFN [Text] Commenting on the decision of the European Union's Council of Foreign Ministers, Alternate Foreign Minister Theodhoros Pangalos said: We do not seek bombings but a peaceful settlement to avoid a repeat of tragic events such as the one last Saturday [5 February]. Our goal is to make peace, not to complicate hostilities.
